---
title: Chicken, Snap Pea and Pineapple Stir-fry with Cashews and Green Onion Rice
description: This Asian-inspired dish features juicy chicken, pineapple, and cashews, served over fluffy green onion jasmine rice. What makes it a winner is the sweet and sour hoisin sauce that brings it all together.
